      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      162.53,
      526.23,
      175.57
    ],
    "text": "punishments were subsequently imposed on them on 29.11.2012 and 04.08.2014,",
