      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      213.53,
      526.22,
      226.57
    ],
    "text": "At the conclusion of the trial, by judgment dated 09.05.2025, the Learned High Court",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      233.33,
      526.12,
      246.37
    ],
    "text": "Judge found the Petitioner along with the 3rd and 5th Accused guilty of the charges and",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      253.13,
      526.49,
      266.17
    ],
    "text": "imposed, for the 1st and 3rd counts, sentences of eight years\u2019 rigorous imprisonment",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      272.96,
      526.3,
      286.0
    ],
    "text": "together with a fine of Rs. 25,000/- and six months\u2019 imprisonment in default for each,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      292.76,
      526.49,
      305.8
    ],
    "text": "ordering the sentences to run concurrently, and further directed payment of Rs. 100,000/-",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      312.68,
      519.89,
      325.72
    ],
    "text": "as compensation to the victim, with a default term of one year\u2019s rigorous imprisonment.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      344.48,
      526.21,
      357.52
    ],
    "text": "I note that the following evidence was presented by the prosecution before the Learned",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      364.28,
      175.53,
      377.32
    ],
    "text": "High Court Judge.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      396.2,
      526.25,
      409.24
    ],
    "text": "On January 18, 1994, at approximately 8:00 a.m., a van bearing registration No. L 300",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      416.0,
      526.35,
      429.04
    ],
    "text": "arrived at A.N. Enterprises, situated near the Maggona filling station in Beruwala. PW1,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      435.8,
      526.49,
      448.84
    ],
    "text": "Nigamuni Sumith Kingsley Mendis, the pump operator, requested the driver to move the",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      455.74,
      526.12,
      468.78
    ],
    "text": "van closer to the diesel pump. At that time, the 5th Accused, together with another",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      475.54,
      526.12,
      488.58
    ],
    "text": "unidentified individual, alighted from the van and proceeded into the office. At that",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      495.34,
      526.49,
      508.38
    ],
    "text": "moment, the Petitioner, who remained inside the van, suddenly opened the door, seized",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      515.14,
      526.2,
      528.18
    ],
    "text": "PW1 by the hand, and forcibly pulled him into the vehicle. Thereafter, the 1st Accused",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      535.06,
      384.98,
      548.1
    ],
    "text": "stabbed the witness and removed the money from his pocket.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      566.86,
      526.33,
      579.9
    ],
    "text": "PW1 remained confined inside the van for about ten minutes before being forcibly ejected.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      586.66,
      526.29,
      599.7
    ],
    "text": "Immediately afterward, the 2nd Accused shouted \u201cLahiru, Lahiru.\u201d At that point, the 5th",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      606.58,
      526.49,
      619.62
    ],
    "text": "Accused, who had been heading toward the office, returned and entered the van.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      626.38,
      526.2,
      639.42
    ],
    "text": "Subsequently, the 3rd Accused, who was the driver, accelerated and drove the vehicle",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      646.21,
      373.22,
      659.25
    ],
    "text": "away from the filling station in the direction of Aluthgama",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      677.29,
      526.2,
      690.33
    ],
    "text": "According to the testimony of PW13, IP Abeyratne Dissanayake, upon receiving a",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      697.21,
      526.35,
      710.25
    ],
    "text": "telephone call regarding the robbery, the police proceeded to the filling station. They then",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      717.01,
      526.23,
      730.05
    ],
    "text": "went to Aluthgama, where they intercepted the vehicle and arrested the 1st and 3rd",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      736.81,
      526.18,
      749.85
    ],
    "text": "Accused. The remaining suspects initially escaped but were subsequently apprehended",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      756.61,
      102.45,
      769.65
    ],
    "text": "later.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
