    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      512.5,
      526.11,
      525.54
    ],
    "text": "It was admitted by the Petitioner that he had gone on a trip with the other accused and,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      532.3,
      526.15,
      545.34
    ],
    "text": "following the incident at the fuel station where he saw PW1 bleeding when he got down",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      552.1,
      526.49,
      565.14
    ],
    "text": "from the van, he shouted at the others to leave as they were drunk; when the police",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      571.9,
      526.36,
      584.94
    ],
    "text": "stopped the vehicle, he alone fled and was arrested the next day. The Learned High Court",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      591.82,
      526.22,
      604.86
    ],
    "text": "Judge, having considered PW1\u2019s evidence that the Petitioner was the person who pulled",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      611.62,
      526.47,
      624.66
    ],
    "text": "the witness into the van while the 1st Accused took the money and later fled, correctly",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      631.42,
      526.22,
      644.46
    ],
    "text": "concluded that the Petitioner shared a common intention with the other accused in",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      651.37,
      454.97,
      664.41
    ],
    "text": "committing the offence of robbery and causing grievous harm to the PW01.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      682.45,
      526.38,
      695.49
    ],
    "text": "I hold that the Learned High Court Judge correctly reached the conclusion in this regard,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      702.25,
      441.38,
      715.29
    ],
    "text": "and there is no reason to interfere with the judgment dated 09.05.2025.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      733.45,
      526.35,
      746.79
    ],
    "text": "For the above\u2011said reasons, I hold that the judgment of the Learned High Court Judge",
    "fonts": [
      "CambriaMath",
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      753.25,
      297.96,
      766.29
    ],
    "text": "does not shock the conscience of this Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      781.3,
      324.89,
      805.78
